Expand through the cloud

Microsoft provides an integrated end-end video streaming solution which supports all common devices from set-top boxes to mobile devices, allowing customers to deliver content with a single integrated workflow and single integrated pay-as-you-go bill.
Optimise productivity
Microsoft provides an easily customisable and scalable platform that delivers improved efficacy, proactive insight, and enhanced collaboration in the cloud or on-premises.
Enhance revenue, reduce cost

Across the media and cable industry, Microsoft delivers an integrated, mission-critical platform that is cloud-ready, to reduce cost-to-income ratios, improve return on assets, and provide the flexible foundation needed for business model transformation.
Cloud support for devices

Creating, managing, and delivering media across multiple devices has never been easier. Media Services provide everything you need to deliver content to a variety of devices, from Xbox and Windows PCs to MacOS, iOS, and Android.
Maintain the connection
Azure Media Services allows you to maintain control of your IP and control the user experience bringing in more views and more revenue.
